text: La Concepción is a corregimiento in Bugaba District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It is the seat of Bugaba District. It has a land area of and had a population of 21,356 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 17,978; its population as of 2000 was 19,330. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
